  <brief_title>Adjuvant Chemotherapy After Preoperative Chemoradiotherapy to Treat Rectal Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Phase II Study of Adjuvant Chemotherapy With 5-FU/Leucovorin vs. Oxaliplatin/5-FU/Leucovorin After Preoperative Chemoradiotherapy With Fluoropyrimidines Followed by Surgery in Patients With Locally Advanced Rectal Cancer</official_title>
