  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Histologically confirmed adenocarcinoma of the rectum

          2. Patients who treated with preoperative chemoradiation with fluoropyrimidines followed
             by curative surgery without microscopic residual tumor.

          3. AJCC/UICC pathologic stages of ypT3-4 or ypN+

          4. Curative surgery not less than 3 and not more than 8 weeks prior to randomization

          5. No prior chemotherapy, radiotherapy and immunotherapy except preoperative
             chemoradiation for rectal cancer

          6. ECOG PS 0-1

          7. Adequate organ function

          8. Informed Consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Macroscopic or microscopic evidence of remaining tumor

          2. Any histologic feature other than adenocarcinoma or arisen from chronic inflammatory
             bowel disease

          3. More than 8 weeks after curative surgery
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
